      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in running order. It requires substantial mechanical work, as the engine has failed and will likely need a full rebuild or replacement. Additionally, the exterior shows significant wear, including several large dents and noticeable rust patches on the wheel arches. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a valuable source of parts for a similar model. Please be prepared to tow the vehicle from its current location.",
      "price": 3500.0,
