    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Unlock the potential of this great project vehicle! While it currently requires some mechanical attention and bodywork to get back to its best, it's the perfect opportunity for a mechanic or hobbyist looking for a rewarding weekend challenge. It's a budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel of a car with plenty of character once you've put in some TLC!",
      "price": 4000.0,
